Insomnia;;77;;92;;R;;From acclaimed director Chris Nolan ("Memento") comes the story of a veteran police detective (Al Pacino) who is sent to a small Alaskan town to investigate the murder of a teenage girl. Forced into a psychological game of cat-and-mouse by the primary suspect (Robin Williams), events escalate and the detective finds his own stability dangerously threatened.;;Mystery & thriller,Crime,Drama;;Christopher Nolan;;2002;;Al Pacino,Robin Williams,Hilary Swank,Maura Tierney,Martin Donovan,Nicky Katt,Paul Dooley,Jonathan Jackson,Larry Holden,Katharine Isabelle;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1114154-insomnia